            <p class="tc-desc">34 pages of policy, and the people who reference it daily need answers in ten seconds. This version strips the reasoning and surfaces the actions: color-coded tiers, inline response steps, and a clear escalation path.</p>
            <p class="tc-desc">Every section tells the reader exactly what to do and who to contact. It's the version a data steward actually keeps open at their desk.</p>
            <a href="/tech-reference" class="teaser-cta">View the full reference &rarr;</a>
